{"tid":7668,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[美帝]在黑色星期五購物日當天Nike海外Outlet裡面居然變成了這慘況...","createTime":"2016-11-28T02:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T01:44:51.000Z","uid":20528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"705777aff5a081f73cabf3d94043915c341dc374","tid":7668,"uid":20528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/static/nomask/files/articles/59952/583a64df1b915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Fstatic%2Fnomask%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F59952%2F583a64df1b915.jpg&h=2546770b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑色星期五 Black Friday 總是提供消費者最低廉的優惠或是限定商品，成為商家、各大品牌的促銷節日，就像光棍節雙 11 般，往往都能創造銷售新高，但這樣的購物熱潮居然在這間 Nike 海外 Outlet 變成了這樣的廢墟，鞋盒散落一地簡直就像是大地震或是喪屍來襲過，讓大家傻眼，只能說店員好苦、消費者素質有待加強...<br />\n<br />\n▼美國黑色星期五 Black Friday 經常讓許多消費者瘋狂搶購，也因為搶購之激烈也經常擦槍走火登上社會新聞，大打出手的場景也經常可以看的到，混亂的場景就像是喪屍來襲...<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/static/nomask/files/articles/59952/583a6596a7d2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Fstatic%2Fnomask%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F59952%2F583a6596a7d2a.jpg&h=945fc73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/static/nomask/files/articles/59952/583a65955c330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Fstatic%2Fnomask%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F59952%2F583a65955c330.jpg&h=0bb01e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/static/nomask/files/articles/59952/583a659766ff6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Fstatic%2Fnomask%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F59952%2F583a659766ff6.jpg&h=b40c4861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼這樣的瘋狂場景也出現在 Nike Outlet，蝗蟲過境般滿地的鞋盒散落一地，實在是很混亂的場景，這樣的消費品質也讓人質疑消費者的素質，畢竟自助式的 Outlet 大家就是要有公德心才對...<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/static/nomask/files/articles/59952/583a64dbd9d69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Fstatic%2Fnomask%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F59952%2F583a64dbd9d69.jpg&h=659c1f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/static/nomask/files/articles/59952/583a64dc9633a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Fstatic%2Fnomask%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F59952%2F583a64dc9633a.jpg&h=1eba5933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/static/nomask/files/articles/59952/583a64dd64619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Fstatic%2Fnomask%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F59952%2F583a64dd64619.jpg&h=072d726a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼黑色星期五 Black Friday 這樣的慘況一點都不誇張，不只是鞋子連衣服也被翻爛，相信當天的店員們應該都相當不爽...錢真難賺...也有人拍下現場影片，的確超誇張。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/static/nomask/files/articles/59952/583a64df1b915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Fstatic%2Fnomask%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F59952%2F583a64df1b915.jpg&h=2546770b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/static/nomask/files/articles/59952/583a64de513de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Fstatic%2Fnomask%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F59952%2F583a64de513de.jpg&h=0017fca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這樣購物的熱潮成功讓店家增加許多營業額，也成功創造話題，在這樣不景氣的年代，消費者們也都精打細算，沒有划算的價格就不會輕易的出手，不過這麼誇張的場景也馬上變成新聞話題。"},{"pid":"75eb91ff4928a7c0deaf3e336a591334b2a82563","tid":7668,"uid":2655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5353c11c56f32bc516f2984e85d4d394719c2bbf","tid":7668,"uid":20528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab588e28aa18792e33da0b459c6fe891ebf2b2a4","tid":7668,"uid":4083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:42:13.000Z","msg":"全球可能只得日本仔重識守秩序"